But this injustice is a result of the injustice the justice system has plagued black lives with. We need love. Not violence. Hear my voice. #BlackLivesMatter

node.text: The team at @plzmatoken is working to solve the huge issue of blood shortage with their own cryptocurrency. Establishing a fiat-crypto bridge with @americanredcross will be cementing them as an extremely legitimate player in the world of cause tokens. Check out plzma.io for more info on what they're all about and a link to swap.
